@startuml
!include _style.puml

title AI Quant 部署视图（Deployment View）

node "开发者机器（macOS）" as dev {
  node "Web (Vite Dev Server)\n:5173" as n_web <<UI>> #ECFDF5
  node "Backend (Uvicorn)\n:8000" as n_api <<API>> #EFF6FF
  node "Streamlit\n:8501" as n_st <<UI>> #ECFDF5
  folder ".ai_quant（本地 Volume）" as vol <<RUNTIME>> #FFF7ED
}

cloud "外部依赖" as ext <<SEC>> #FEE2E2 {
  node "MySQL\n:3306" as mysql <<DB>> #EFF6FF
  node "LLM/Embedding\n(DashScope)" as dash <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
  node "Web Search\n(Tavily)" as tavily <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
  node "QMT Gateway\n(Windows 云端)" as qmt <<SEC>> #FEE2E2
}

n_web --> n_api : /api/*（Vite proxy）
n_st --> n_api : /api/agent/run
n_api --> vol : logs/outputs/index
n_api --> mysql : 读取 trade_* 表
n_api --> dash : 研报/Embedding（可选）
n_api --> tavily : deepseek 时 web_search（可选）
n_api --> qmt : /api/trading/*（转发，X-API-Token）

note right of vol
容器化/上云时建议将 `.ai_quant`\n作为独立挂载卷，便于备份与迁移
end note

@enduml
